rooms.roomDescription: Come Together And Savor The Warmth Of Good Food And Great Company In An Inviting Dining Room, Underneath A Beautiful Hand-Picked Chandelier, Where Every Meal Feels Like A Comforting Hug.
The Room's Layout Allows For A Seamless Blend Of Relaxation And Recreation, Offering A Versatile And Harmonious Space For Both Rest And Play.  Play Area Has Additional Lighting Installed.

The Bedroom Features A Designated Sleeping Area With High Vaulted Ceilings.  The Master Bedroom Boasts A Luxurious Open Bathroom Concept, Seamlessly Integrated To Create An Indulgent Spa-Like Retreat.  The Chadelier Is For Decoration Purposes Only!

The Open Bathroom Area, Defined By Refined Finishes And Modern Design, Includes A Spacious Single Vanity. The Toilet And Shower Are Tucked Away In A Separate, Private Enclosure Providing Additional Privacy And Functionality.  Adjacent To The Bathroom, A Well-Organized And Expansive Walk-In Closet Offers Ample Storage And Organization.

The Space Offers A Blank Canvas For Future Development, With Exposed Piping And Electrical Fixtures Hinting At The Possibilities For A Fully Customized Transformation. Large, Open Areas And High Ceilings Provide A Sense Of Spaciousness, Inviting The Imagination To Envision The Potential For A Future Recreation Room, Home Gym, Or Additional Living Space.

data.description:
This updated three-story home features high vaulted ceilings, providing an open and spacious feel throughout the house. The home boasts four bedrooms, ideal for accommodating a family or guests, along with three well-appointed bathrooms for convenience and privacy. With two living room spaces, there's plenty of room for relaxation and entertainment, while the dining room offers a perfect setting for shared meals and special occasions. The open kitchen concept adds a modern touch, allowing for easy interaction and flow between the kitchen and living areas. Custom front doors and glass patio doors enhance the home's aesthetic appeal while welcoming natural light inside. The use of luxury vinyl plank (LVP) flooring offers durability and a sleek, contemporary look. Additionally, the unfinished basement provides ample potential for customization and expansion, allowing the homeowner to tailor the space to their specific needs and preferences.

Backyard has been upgraded with artificial turf, saving you thousands per year on your water bill!

This home is situated in a well-known, tranquil community, offering a perfect blend of peace and convenience. Its location near highway 225 and highway 25 provides easy access to major transportation arteries, facilitating seamless travel to various destinations. Additionally, the proximity to public transportation, including the light rail, ensures accessibility to urban amenities and entertainment options. 

Furthermore, the home's location near the DTC (Denver Tech Center) area and Cherry Creek Reservoir presents an attractive opportunity for residents to enjoy business, recreational, and outdoor activities within a short distance. These nearby attractions make the location highly desirable for individuals seeking both a peaceful residential environment and easy access to urban and natural amenities.
